Environment: OS: Windows 10 Pro v. 21H1 19043.1237, Browser: Opera GX LVL4 (core: 99.0.4788.49).
Steps to reproduce
1. Go to the account dashboard page
2. Click on the Invite a new user button
3. Enter into the email field: any email with unicode characters.
Actual result: System validates the email as correct
Expected result: The email with unicode characters should not be validated as correct
Severity: Low
Priority: Low
Additional info: The problem is present for other email inputs
